===Pronunciation===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
חוילה / chăvîylâh / khav-ee-law'

===Etymology===
Probably from {{HH|2342}}; 

===Proper noun===
'''חוילה'''

# circular; Chavilah, the name of two or three eastern regions; also perhaps of two men: - Havilah.

